        <p style="text-align: left;">Simply, you dream... and we create...<br>The delicate journey between dreaming the event, gathering ideas, handpicking the best venue options, and creating it in the most desired way within the planned budget is our major talent.<br>Turkey Weddings is one of the well-known bespoke event planners in Turkey, specialized in destination weddings, legal civil ceremonies as well as parties, celebrations, <a href="#" hidefocus="true" style="outline: none;">beach weddings</a>,&nbsp;and other private events.<br>Getting married is one of the most significant milestones in people’s lives and the adventure starts with an ‘I do’ ('evet' in <em>Turkish</em>) for a lifetime.<br>You only tell us about their dream wedding. Where do you dream of yourself for your big day?<br>Where would be the best place for that big YES word?<br>What kind of a place/venue you are looking for at the desired destination?<br>The coolest? The most romantic? The most popular or as secluded as possible?<br>Does it have to be the most flashy or humble but elegant?<br>Don't worry, it will look great on your <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" hidefocus="true" style="outline: none;">Instagram</a> anyway :-)<br>We are dedicated to style unforgettable moments with the beloved ones &amp; families in the highlighted destinations. Our team knows how to plan the big day and served many couples of different nationalities for destination weddings until today. We suggest unique wedding ideas and propose different wedding venues and locations. Contact us for beach wedding ideas, palatial wedding ideas, thematic wedding ideas (or simply name your dream theme), vintage wedding ideas all around Turkey. Turkey Weddings is a one-stop-shop to create your dream wedding ceremony with an all-inclusive package. With an all-inclusive package, we process the legal paperwork and assist you all the way through the civil marriage procedure as well as creating your dream ceremony by assigning the proper subcontractors for music, decorations, photography, hair, make-up, wedding cake, wedding dinner, etc. We would be happy to help you with your honeymoon arrangements if you like.<br>We plan and tailor elegant, stylish, and glamorous weddings created with unique ceremony ideas at some secret heavens as well as at popular spots with fun and exquisite celebrating options.<br>We are highly-qualified awarded planners for savvy and sophisticated couples who demand genuine service and diligence. Whether you are visiting our website for your celebration in mind or an international marriage, for getting married in Turkey, or just taking a look around; we hope a tour inside will be inspiring.</p>    </div>
